Cyber-Doc
A Cyber-Doc is a specialist in cybernetic surgery and bionic modification, as
well as conventional medicine. They are the only characters with the training
to install cybernetics in the field and are in high demand across the Rifts
wastelands from mercenary units and wealthy clients alike.

Cyber-Docs choose from Medical, Technical, and Physical skill categories.
Their medical knowledge rivals the Body Fixer but their focus is the interface
of technology and biology.

Attribute requirements: IQ 12, ME 8.
Starting equipment: Full surgical kit, portable cybernetics installation tools,
medical scanner, drug kit, first aid supplies, and a concealed sidearm.
